Scrapy escapes URL fragments using AJAX escaping scheme. If you want to pass a URL with a fragment to Splash then set url in args dict manually:

```py
url = 'http://example.com#id2'
yield scrapy.Request(url, meta={
    'splash': {'args': {'url': url}}
})
```

I've documented it here: https://github.com/scrapy-plugins/scrapy-splash/commit/df63383a8fe96fb521e1d9035785d01d53d825d5. Sorry for the confusion.

